IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. PolicyEngine.

ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.

DATA DIVISION.
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
01 WS-POLICY-ID     PIC 9(6).
01 WS-ACTION        PIC X(10).
01 WS-RESULT        PIC X(200).
01 WS-PREMIUM       PIC 9(9)V99.
01 WS-FACTOR        PIC 9(3)V99.
01 WS-FINAL         PIC 9(9)V99.

LINKAGE SECTION.
01 LK-POLICY-ID     PIC 9(6).
01 LK-ACTION        PIC X(10).
01 LK-PREMIUM       PIC 9(9)V99.
01 LK-PRODUCT       PIC X(20).
01 LK-RESULT        PIC X(200).

PROCEDURE DIVISION USING LK-POLICY-ID LK-ACTION
                         LK-PREMIUM LK-PRODUCT LK-RESULT.

    MOVE LK-POLICY-ID TO WS-POLICY-ID.
    MOVE LK-ACTION    TO WS-ACTION.

    EVALUATE WS-ACTION
        WHEN 'RATING   '
            EVALUATE TRUE
                WHEN LK-PRODUCT(1:10) = 'LIFE-BASIC'
                    MOVE 1.10 TO WS-FACTOR
                WHEN LK-PRODUCT(1:9)  = 'LIFE-PLUS'
                    MOVE 1.25 TO WS-FACTOR
                WHEN LK-PRODUCT(1:12) = 'HEALTH-BASIC'
                    MOVE 1.15 TO WS-FACTOR
                WHEN OTHER
                    MOVE 1.20 TO WS-FACTOR
            END-EVALUATE
            COMPUTE WS-FINAL = LK-PREMIUM * WS-FACTOR
            MOVE WS-FINAL TO LK-PREMIUM
            STRING 'RATING OK FACTOR=' WS-FACTOR
                   ' FINAL=' WS-FINAL
                   DELIMITED SIZE INTO LK-RESULT

        WHEN 'VALIDATE '
            IF LK-PREMIUM > 0 AND LK-PRODUCT NOT = SPACES
                MOVE 'POLICY VALID' TO LK-RESULT
            ELSE
                MOVE 'ERROR: INVALID POLICY DATA' TO LK-RESULT
            END-IF

        WHEN 'CLAIMCHK '
            IF LK-PREMIUM > 1000000
                MOVE 'WARNING: HIGH VALUE CLAIM - REVIEW REQUIRED'
                    TO LK-RESULT
            ELSE
                MOVE 'CLAIM AMOUNT OK' TO LK-RESULT
            END-IF

        WHEN OTHER
            MOVE 'ERROR: UNKNOWN ACTION' TO LK-RESULT
    END-EVALUATE.

    GOBACK.